jai &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( english : hail the water of the ganges ) is a 2016 indian hindi crime drama film , directed by prakash jha . it is a follow-up to the 2003 crime film &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and stars priyanka chopra in the lead role with jha appearing in a supporting role . it also features manav kaul , rahul bhat , and queen harish . the film was released worldwide on 4 march 2016 . the government of madhya pradesh declared jai &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; tax-free on 9 march 2016 .